{"tid":814123,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"無悔加入Dansoc　大學女生：跳性感舞蹈不等於壞女孩","createTime":"2018-09-11T04:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T18:43:12.000Z","uid":58335,"like":15,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ec99b6498cb39dbe9cf4d3d62795e358f5afcae8","tid":814123,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"大家點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1454065/org/f8411a1fa9ef6b3c033f9ee6e872e934.png/8kqG35i_aaLXODCuzFq3lirkS7D4WpjMbAb9lGwG_ZQ?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1454065%2Forg%2Ff8411a1fa9ef6b3c033f9ee6e872e934.png%2F8kqG35i_aaLXODCuzFq3lirkS7D4WpjMbAb9lGwG_ZQ%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=42cf84c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前，有網民將港大聯堂舞蹈匯演的照片上載至討論區，舞蹈員的性感尺度引起不少爭議，留言一面倒認為表演過於意淫，甚至「影衰HKU」。<br />\n<br />\n今次《開罐Opener》邀請了兩位跳舞女生現身說法，她們均參加過大學舞蹈學會，其中一位更是港大聯堂舞蹈匯演的表演者之一。<br />\n<br />\nMinerva曾經參加過港大的舞蹈學會（Dansoc），<br />\n同時亦是宿舍施德龍堂的活躍分子，<br />\n今年有份參與聯堂舞蹈匯演。<br />\n作品的主題是洗澡，<br />\n加上性感的服裝，<br />\n令她們備受抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1434181/org/81ee57453e351f61ba0195af231d5c1a.jpeg/Qf8EzKbg3kwwpaMX-2O62nuCT-A-aUfJGekqvhnpKr4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1434181%2Forg%2F81ee57453e351f61ba0195af231d5c1a.jpeg%2FQf8EzKbg3kwwpaMX-2O62nuCT-A-aUfJGekqvhnpKr4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=23ccff53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跳舞志在抒發情感<br />\n<br />\n「很多網民說我們是臭雞（妓女），<br />\n私下一定是個不檢點的女生。」<br />\n網民的無情批評令Minerva十分無奈。<br />\n她認為每個人都會有情慾，<br />\n而她們只是將這個情感<br />\n透過舞蹈表達出來。<br />\n<br />\n「如果你令他聯想起性行為，<br />\n其實是另類的讚美。」<br />\n樂觀的Minerva說道。<br />\n<br />\n跳舞如演戲<br />\n<br />\nLuxi認為網民不應以一個作品，<br />\n去判斷一個人的本質。<br />\n她曾經參與過較性感的表演，<br />\n舞蹈員的角色是表達歌曲的感覺。<br />\n「跟其他行業其實沒有太大分別，<br />\n例如演員根據劇本演繹性感橋段，<br />\n難道演員私下也是妓女嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1434186/org/332042fa14b319f3601d0b58b7dd0d81.jpeg/P1lkNGBEuFXM8cTof0EcFHCeYc6mA9Jx-SltmPkpbZg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1434186%2Forg%2F332042fa14b319f3601d0b58b7dd0d81.jpeg%2FP1lkNGBEuFXM8cTof0EcFHCeYc6mA9Jx-SltmPkpbZg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=85d389ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n既然每人的想法和觀值觀都不一樣，<br />\nLuxi亦不打算討好全部人。<br />\n所以，<br />\n網民的負評不會改變她對跳舞的熱誠。<br />\n<br />\nDansoc不等於壞學生<br />\n<br />\n相信在學或已畢業的大專生，<br />\n對舞蹈學會（Dansoc）的印象不外乎<br />\n「好chur」、「爛grade」、<br />\n「唔返學」等。<br />\nDansoc生活雖然非常忙碌，<br />\n令她們經常沒有時間休息，<br />\n但絕對不是外界所說的「Freerider」。<br />\n<br />\n「很多人盡自己學生的責任，<br />\n同時盡舞蹈員的責任。」<br />\nMinerva笑言，<br />\n四年的大學生涯以來<br />\n沒有一科不合格，<br />\n而Luxi亦順利準時畢業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1434461/org/77b485876c31df4973e1bba6148b2e18.jpg/L7m5M5K_UwyEWNf3nJQ-4TfqmuRFDaP0CEMrjghDK44?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1434461%2Forg%2F77b485876c31df4973e1bba6148b2e18.jpg%2FL7m5M5K_UwyEWNf3nJQ-4TfqmuRFDaP0CEMrjghDK44%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=caf64378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多重身份學會堅持<br />\n<br />\n「讀書是學生的責任，<br />\n但不是學生的全部。」<br />\nLuxi認為發展興趣<br />\n可以令學生有書本以外的得著，<br />\n例如堅持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「參加Dansoc要練舞、<br />\n訓練體能、準備舞台道具，<br />\n同時又要上課、<br />\n交功課和溫書，<br />\n辛苦程度難以想像。」<br />\n意志力不夠強的人<br />\n是無法克服鐵人般的生活。<br />\n<br />\n雖然過程辛苦，<br />\n但她們都從未後悔過參加Dansoc。<br />\n因為Dansoc令她們學懂堅持，<br />\n這是最難能可貴的得著。<br />\nDansoc生活對她們來說，<br />\n是青春中很重要的印記。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/186955/%E7%84%A1%E6%82%94%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5dansoc-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F-%E8%B7%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F%E8%88%9E%E8%B9%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E6%96%BC%E5%A3%9E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F186955%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2582%2594%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5dansoc-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F-%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%2588%259E%25E8%25B9%2588%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25A3%259E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25A9&d=G6Do748NN7a8wppDrpWp16WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7e73e246\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/186955/%E7%84%A1%E6%82%94%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5dansoc-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F-%E8%B7%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F%E8%88%9E%E8%B9%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E6%96%BC%E5%A3%9E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9</a>"},{"pid":"ed7f77283fcc33eb1933dc97d51375001771c45e","tid":814123,"uid":11464,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"bbc66df80fcd895f003f97c51287f45d03f06ade","tid":814123,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"識人有份跳毛巾舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時睇唔出"},{"pid":"5bf3bfa36a0b18ccdc9d72c891bff9f779851390","tid":814123,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bbc66df80fcd895f003f97c51287f45d03f06ade","tid":814123,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"識人有份跳毛巾舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時睇唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"平時好斯文??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ca3f2440841e37cb1d1416c964f1e1fa253f7b","tid":814123,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5bf3bfa36a0b18ccdc9d72c891bff9f779851390","tid":814123,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bbc66df80fcd895f003f97c51287f45d03f06ade","tid":814123,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"識人有份跳毛巾舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時睇唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"平時好斯文??<img